{# Generic Document Template
   Purpose: Flexible template for ad-hoc documentation (migration guides, references, etc.)
   Tier: Concrete (no inheritance - standalone template)
   
   Required variables:
   - title: Document title
   - purpose: Brief purpose statement
   - issue_number: Related GitHub issue number
   
   Optional variables:
   - date: Document creation/update date
   - breaking_changes: Breaking changes notice
   - scope_in: What is in scope
   - scope_out: What is out of scope
   - related_docs: List of related document paths
   - custom_sections: List of {heading, content} dicts
#}
